# Frontend Rules

## Component Structure
- Client components: `'use client'` at top + useState/useEffect allowed
- Server components: no directive needed, no hooks, async functions ok
- Name files: PascalCase for components, kebab-case for pages

## Tailwind Patterns
- Profit margin display: bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-lg p-4
- Stock badge: green=in stock | amber=low stock | red=out of stock
- Modal backdrop: `fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 z-50`
- Sidebar active item: `bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 border-r-2 border-blue-600`

## Profit Margin (Always show in product forms)
Show when both price and cost are filled:
- Calculate: ((price - cost) / cost * 100).toFixed(1)%
- Display in bg-green-50 card with TrendingUp icon

## Toast Notifications
- Success: `toast.success('Mensaje')`
- Error: `toast.error('Mensaje')`  
- Position: bottom-right
- After success: `router.refresh()`
